description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 6 Episode 21

In another twist in the competition, teams are set to prove their worth for a chance to stay in the race for the main prize. Hosted by Pete Evans and Manu Feildel.

In a redemption challenge round, featuring the bottom 6 teams from the early rounds.

Tonight, Victorian housemates Jane and Emma are aiming for a vast improvement at their second instant restaurant. Will it be easy with organised Jane's agenda or will the stress override her plans again?
